def show_image(image_path):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
    plt.imshow(plt.imread(image_path), cmap="gray")
    plt.grid()
    plt.title(image_path)
    plt.show()

def get_line_equation(x1, y1, x2, y2):
    a = (y2-y1)/(x2-x1)
    b = y1 - a*x1
    return a, b

def plot_line(x1, y1, x2, y2, color):
    a, b = get_line_equation(x1, y1, x2, y2)
    x = np.linspace(0, 150, 150)
    y = a*x + b
    plt.plot(x, y, color)
    plt.imshow(img_c, cmap="gray")
    return a, b

def show_image_with_line(image_path, a, b, pixels):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
    image = plt.imread(image_path)
    image = image[350:700, 700:1200]
    plt.imshow(image, cmap="gray")
    x = np.linspace(0, image.shape[1], image.shape[1])
    y = a*x + b
    yb = a*x + b+ pixels
    yt = a*x + b- pixels
    plt.plot(x, y, "red")
    plt.plot(x, yb, "g")
    plt.plot(x, yt, 'white')
    plt.grid()
    plt.title(image_path)
    plt.show()
